  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was probably a very dirty way of working over there, It was money, to be inside, and so on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But probably, I-- I would like to mention Mr.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Pemper, Mietek Pemper, who was a secretary of Goeth.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "One of Jewish secretaries. but he was so [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] clever that when Goeth said something what had to be he had to he couldn't know about it, he was asking one of the German writers to write the letters.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Mr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Pemper was proving a new [NON-ENGLISH], you have to help me, how does it, called--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, is very little mention about him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a a witness for Goeth, to get in the Krakow court.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's where, I believe, [BACKROUND NOISE] that happened, all of a sudden, from 300, we have 1,100 or 1,200.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we had the the the the the stuff, the same stuff that we had been before the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not the same people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I'll tell you, there was-- there was a very dirty word.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was-- I couldn't I couldn't tell you why he had taken such a risk.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know how to explain it now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know what his mind was in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because-- how long we had been working at Emalia he was making money with us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When he'd been in Brunnlitz, there was no production at all.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Coming back back to that that one was-- [PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] He was getting from the German Wehrmacht some money, how long-- how he progressed, to prepare the factory to work.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I tell you, those were in-- '40- '45, about there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He approached me, in you know from the seeing what I had-- done, or said something.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
